snippet.title: Seafight: League of Captains - Commissioning and Commanding!
snippet.description:
Listen up, pirates! Now you can take captains aboard, commission them, and use their powerful maneuvers to turn the tide of every battle! 
But that’s not all! Brand-new captains, as well as some general improvements, are ready to be explored, too! Are yer fingers twitchin’? Then set sail towards the new and improved League of Captains!
